flowchart TB
    Source[(源数据库)]
    Target[(目标数据库)]

    subgraph fullPath [全量数据路径]
        direction LR
        R[Reader] --> Ch[Channel]
        Ch --> W[Writer]
    end

    subgraph incrPath [增量数据路径]
        direction LR
        Log[变更日志] --> Store[Store]
        Store --> Q[Record队列]
        Q --> Incr[IncrSync]
    end

    subgraph verifyPath [校验数据路径]
        direction LR
        V[FullVerification] --> Diff[差异报告与订正SQL]
    end

    Source --> R
    Source --> Log
    W --> Target
    Incr --> Target
    Source --> V
    Target --> V
